<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(٤٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{النَّشْأَةَ الْأُخْرَى}</span> ... إِعَادَةَ خَلْقِهِمْ بَعْدَ فَنَائِهِمْ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(٤٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَغْنَى وَأَقْنَى}</span> ... مَلَّكَهُمُ الأَمْوَالَ، وَأَرْضَاهُمْ بِمَا أَعْطَاهُمْ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٤٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الشِّعْرَى}</span> ... نَجْمٍ مُضِيءٍ كَانَ أَهْلُ الجَاهِلِيَّةِ يَعْبُدُونَهُ مِنْ دُونِ اللهِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٥٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{عَادًا الْأُولَى}</span> ... قَوْمَ هُودٍ - عليه السلام -.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٥١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَثَمُودَ}</span> ... قَوْمَ صَالِحٍ - عليه السلام -.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٥٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَالْمُؤْتَفِكَةَ}</span> ... مَدَائِنَ قَوْمِ لُوطٍ - عليه السلام -، سُمِّيَتْ بِذَلِكَ؛ لِأَنَّ اللهَ قَلَبَهَا عَلَى أَهْلِهَا.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٥٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَهْوَى}</span> ... أَسْقَطَهَا إِلَى الأَرْضِ بَعْدَ رَفْعِهَا.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٥٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَغَشَّاهَا}</span> ... فَأَلْبَسَهَا مِنَ الحِجَارَةِ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٥٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{آلَاءِ رَبِّكَ}</span> ... نِقَمِ رَبِّكَ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٥٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{تَتَمَارَى}</span> ... تَتَشَكَّكُ أَيُّهَا الإِنْسَانُ المُكَذِّبُ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٥٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{هَذَا نَذِيرٌ}</span> ... مُحَمَّدٌ - صلى الله عليه وسلم - مُنْذِرٌ بِالحَقِّ كَمَنْ سَبَقَهُ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(٥٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَزِفَتْ}</span> ... قَرُبَتْ، وَدَنَا وَقْتُهَا.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(٥٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْآزِفَةُ}</span> ... القِيَامَةُ، سُمِّيَتْ بِذَلِكَ؛ لِقُرْبِ مِيعَادِهَا.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(٥٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{كَاشِفَةٌ}</span> ... نَفْسٌ تَدْفَعُ أَهْوَالَهَا، وَتَطَّلِعُ عَلَى وَقْتِ وُقُوعِهَا.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(٦١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{سَامِدُونَ}</span> ... لَاهُونَ، مُعْرِضُونَ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>